My dotfile repo
###


To use:
###

	git clone --bare <git-repo-url> $HOME/Workspace/coryleeio/dotfiles

	alias config='/usr/bin/git --git-dir=$HOME/Workspace/coryleeio/dotfiles/ --work-tree=$HOME'

	config checkout

	config config --local status.showUntrackedFiles no


Move offending files to .config-backup
###
	mkdir -p .config-backup && \
	config checkout 2>&1 | egrep "\s+\." | awk {'print $1'} | \
	xargs -I{} mv {} .config-backup/{}A


Original setup guide
###

	https://www.atlassian.com/git/tutorials/dotfiles
